query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `projects` (
  `id` int AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
  `userId` int NOT NULL,
  `name` varchar(255) NOT NULL,
  `description` text,
  `prompt` text,
  `status` enum('draft','published','archived') DEFAULT 'draft' NOT NULL,
  `thumbnail` varchar(512),
  `createdAt` timestamp DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
  `updatedAt` timestamp DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `designs` (
  `id` int AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
  `projectId` int NOT NULL,
  `version` int DEFAULT 1 NOT NULL,
  `name` varchar(255) NOT NULL,
  `designData` json NOT NULL,
  `designTokens` json NOT NULL,
  `metadata` json,
  `createdAt` timestamp DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
  `updatedAt` timestamp DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
  FOREIGN KEY (`projectId`) REFERENCES `projects`(`id`)
);

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `exports` (
  `id` int AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
  `projectId` int NOT NULL,
  `designId` int NOT NULL,
  `exportType` enum('framer','figma','webflow','html') NOT NULL,
  `fileUrl` varchar(512) NOT NULL,
  `fileKey` varchar(512) NOT NULL,
  `exportData` json,
  `createdAt` timestamp DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
  FOREIGN KEY (`projectId`) REFERENCES `projects`(`id`),
  FOREIGN KEY (`designId`) REFERENCES `designs`(`id`)
);

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `templates` (
  `id` int AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
  `name` varchar(255) NOT NULL,
  `category` varchar(100) NOT NULL,
  `description` text,
  `thumbnail` varchar(512),
  `templateData` json NOT NULL,
  `designTokens` json NOT NULL,
  `isPublic` int DEFAULT 1 NOT NULL,
  `createdAt` timestamp DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
  `updatedAt` timestamp DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `generatedImages` (
  `id` int AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
  `projectId` int NOT NULL,
  `prompt` text NOT NULL,
  `imageUrl` varchar(512) NOT NULL,
  `imageKey` varchar(512) NOT NULL,
  `metadata` json,
  `createdAt` timestamp DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
  FOREIGN KEY (`projectId`) REFERENCES `projects`(`id`)
);

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `projectAssets` (
  `id` int AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
  `projectId` int NOT NULL,
  `assetType` enum('image','font','icon','video','document') NOT NULL,
  `fileName` varchar(255) NOT NULL,
  `fileUrl` varchar(512) NOT NULL,
  `fileKey` varchar(512) NOT NULL,
  `fileSize` int,
  `mimeType` varchar(100),
  `metadata` json,
  `createdAt` timestamp DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
  FOREIGN KEY (`projectId`) REFERENCES `projects`(`id`)
);
